// 1. Added "public" keyword to all functions to make them callable from outside the contract.
// 2. Replaced "tx.origin" with "msg.sender" in the onlyOwner modifier for enhanced security.
// 3. Added "require" statement in the CashOut function to check if the user has sufficient balance before transferring funds.
// 4. Replaced the external call in the CashOut function with the "transfer" method to prevent reentrancy attacks.
